params.sqlcmd: "SELECT " +" A.\\"SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO\\" AS \\"SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO\\", " +" A.SHIP_INVOICE_NO, " +" A.CUST_CD, " +" G.CUST_NAME, " +" TO_CHAR(A.SHIP_PLAN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH:MM') AS \\"SHIP_PLAN_DATE\\", " +" A.SHIP_NO, " +" A.DLV_LOC_CD, " +" A.DEPARTURE_PLACE, " +" TO_CHAR(A.DEPARTURE_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" A.ARRIVAL_PLACE, " +" TO_CHAR(A.ARRIVAL_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" A.REMARKS_1, " +" A.REMARKS_2, " +" A.TAX_INCLUDE_AMOUNT, " +" A.INVOICE_TAX_AMOUNT, " +" A.TAX_CREDIT_AMOUNT, " +" I.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" J.\\"CUST_ITEM_NAME\\" AS \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" I.\\"CUST_ODR_NO\\" AS \\"ODR_NO\\", " +" I.SHIP_QTY, " +" I.UNIT_PRICE, " +" I.SHIP_ODR_AMOUNT " +"FROM " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD A, " +" M_CUST G, " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_DETAIL I, " +" M_ITEM_SPEC J " +"WHERE " +" A.CUST_CD = G.CUST_CD " +" AND A.SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO = I.SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO " +" AND I.CUST_ITEM_CD = J.CUST_ITEM_CD " +" AND A.CUST_CD = J.CUST_CD " +" AND G.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND A.CUST_CD = ? " +" AND A.DLV_LOC_CD = ? " +" AND A.SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO = ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(A.CREATED_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') >= ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(A.CREATED_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') <= ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(A.SHIP_PLAN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH:MM') >= ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(A.SHIP_PLAN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH:MM') <= ? " +" AND A.PRINT_FLG = ? " +"ORDER BY " +" A.CUST_CD, " +" A.DLV_LOC_CD, " +" A.SHIP_PLAN_DATE, " +" A.SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO, " +" I.ODR_NO"

"SELECT " +" COUNT(1) " +"FROM " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD A, " +" M_CUST G, " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_DETAIL I, " +" M_ITEM J " +"WHERE " +" A.CUST_CD = G.CUST_CD " +" AND A.SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO = I.SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO " +" AND I.ITEM_CD = J.ITEM_CD " +" AND G.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND A.CUST_CD = ? " +" AND A.DLV_LOC_CD = ? " +" AND A.SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO = ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(A.CREATED_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') >= ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(A.CREATED_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') <= ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(A.SHIP_PLAN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH:MM') >= ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(A.SHIP_PLAN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH:MM') <= ? " +" AND A.PRINT_FLG = ?"
"SELECT " +" M_CUST.\\"CUST_CD\\" AS \\"CUST_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" M_CUST " +"WHERE " +" M_CUST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_CUST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" A.\\"SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO\\" AS \\"SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO\\", " +" A.SHIP_INVOICE_NO, " +" A.CUST_CD, " +" G.CUST_NAME, " +" TO_CHAR(A.SHIP_PLAN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH:MM') AS \\"SHIP_PLAN_DATE\\", " +" A.SHIP_NO, " +" A.DLV_LOC_CD, " +" A.DEPARTURE_PLACE, " +" TO_CHAR(A.DEPARTURE_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" A.ARRIVAL_PLACE, " +" TO_CHAR(A.ARRIVAL_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" A.REMARKS_1, " +" A.REMARKS_2, " +" A.TAX_INCLUDE_AMOUNT, " +" A.INVOICE_TAX_AMOUNT, " +" A.TAX_CREDIT_AMOUNT, " +" I.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" J.\\"CUST_ITEM_NAME\\" AS \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" I.\\"CUST_ODR_NO\\" AS \\"ODR_NO\\", " +" I.SHIP_QTY, " +" I.UNIT_PRICE, " +" I.SHIP_ODR_AMOUNT " +"FROM " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD A, " +" M_CUST G, " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_DETAIL I, " +" M_CUST_ITEM J " +"WHERE " +" A.CUST_CD = G.CUST_CD " +" AND A.SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO = I.SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO " +" AND I.CUST_ITEM_CD = J.CUST_ITEM_CD " +" AND A.CUST_CD = J.CUST_CD " +" AND G.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND A.CUST_CD = ? " +" AND A.DLV_LOC_CD = ? " +" AND A.SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO = ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(A.CREATED_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') >= ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(A.CREATED_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') <= ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(A.SHIP_PLAN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH:MM') >= ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(A.SHIP_PLAN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH:MM') <= ? " +" AND A.PRINT_FLG = ? " +"ORDER BY " +" A.CUST_CD, " +" A.DLV_LOC_CD, " +" A.SHIP_PLAN_DATE, " +" A.SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO, " +" I.ODR_NO"
